        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. Participate in one Lair Reive in Yorcia Weald.\n   - You may join the reive in the middle of the battle as long as you are present for the final evaluation.\n2. Lair Reives can be found at the following locations:\n   - (F/G-7) - 2 Loyal Snapweed and 3 Furibund Rafflesia - Bivouac #3\n     - Exit North run straight east and take the first left.\n   - (H/I-6) - 2 Tight-lipped Flytraps and 2 Tenacious Panopts - Bivouac #1\n     - Exit North until you pass 2 Saptraps and head east you\'ll pass 2 Snapweeds. Take a right and head East again to find some Leaflick Lapinion, and eventually find some Cheeky Opo-opo and Saptraps. It\'s just north from there a bit.\n   - (J/K-6) - 2 Loyal Snapweed and 2 Tenacious Panopts - Frontier Station\n     - Exit to West heading north through the log. Take the first right at the Snapweeds. Next, left just after the next hallow log, right at the 4 Snapweeds, and right at the 2 Corpse Flowers and 2 Snapweeds.\nYou\'ll enter a big "Room" with 4 Corpse flowers and the Reive at the back.\n   - (K-9) - 2 Fervid Funguar and 2 Tight-lipped Flytraps - Frontier Station\n     - Exit southeast and hold the left wall. You\'ll get there eventually.\n   - (J-11) - 2 Fervid Funguar and 2 Furibund Rafflesia - Bivouac #2\n     - Exit and head past the path on the north near the 2 Saplings and the Snapweed till you see a path that heads south near a Droughted Treant. You\'ll come to a T intersection with with a 3rd Treant. Head East from thereand the path will slowly point SE as you pass Saptraps and Snapweeds. You should come across a hallowed out log. Head on through and on the south end of this room you should find the Reive.',
