        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. Obtain a number of Hatchets, or, preferably, Trailblazing Hatchet +1s.\n   - Bring a large number. The break rate for HELM tools in Adoulin areas is very high, even with the key items from Kithvalio occasionally preventing tool breakage.\n2. Travel to Ceizak Battlegrounds or Yahse Hunting Grounds\n3. Locate Logging Points and use the Hatchet:\nCeizak Battlegrounds: E8, F8, F10, H7, J8\n4. Repeat until you\'ve obtained five items.\n   - Note that gathering fatigue sets rather quickly, depending on various conditions such as Ionis effects.\n   - Fatigue slowly decays over time, allowing one additional successful gathering attempt approximately every two minutes.\n   - Fatigue also completely resets when you change zones.\n5. You do not need to keep the items you obtained during the assignment. You can safely toss or sell any HELM results and still complete the assignment.',
