        walkthrough = '1. Travel to Rala Waterways and fight Plantpassage Slugs there until they utilize the Fuscous Ooze special attack.\n   - These are located in the South-East part of Rala Waterways, which is most easily accessed from (F-7) Eastern Adoulin. (the south-east entrance/exit seems like it will never be implemented, unfortunately)\n2. After being hit with Fuscous Ooze, the assignment will be complete.\n   - Fuscous Ooze is a conal attack, and will clear this assignment for anyone who gets hit with it.\n3. It is possible to bring one or both of the Plantpassage Slugs from the L/M-8 area to the F-7 Eastern Adoulin entrance to Rala Waterways\n   - You will aggro all the mobs on the way back. It may be best to have a friend sleep the Plantpassage Slug once you reach the entrance and let the other adds despawn after you get KOd or you zone out.\n4. To optimize time, bank imprimaturs in other coalition assignments (canceling will return them to you) until you can do 6-7 runs in a row (20+ imprimaturs) to complete Petitioner rank\n   - If one person holds the Plantpassage Slug, you can clear the assignment, Warp II to Western Adoulin HP #1, Waypoint #3 to Mummers, turn in/get new assignment, Waypoint to Eastern Adoulin #4, and enter again, repeating until you rank up.\n   - The Slug family only has three TP moves, so you can let it get TP from hitting you or by hitting it with a spell like Dia.',
        notes = nil,
    },
