        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. Fight Snapweed in Yorcia Weald until the Tickling Tendrils special attack is used.\n2. After being hit with Stun effect from Tickling Tendrils, the assignment will be complete.\n   - A shield being equipped can block the move.\n   - The move is single target, so if doing for multiple characters, each will need to be the target of the attack.\n3. There are Snapweeds located directly north of Bivouac #3.',
